HEADWORD: Housework
<hw>House"work`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The work belonging
to housekeeping; especially, kitchen work, sweeping, scrubbing, bed
making, and the like.</def>⟦br⟧
